Firefighters extinguish an Antonov-24 passenger plane, which burst into flames after crash landing into a sewage treatment plant during an emergency landing, in the Eastern Siberian town of Nizhneangarsk, Russia on Thursday. The accident killed two crew members, and 22 out of the 42 passengers were injured. Photo: IC  
